Furthermore, multiple different
organizations may be using the same

5
00:00:10,006 --> 00:00:11,621
cloud computing environment.

6
00:00:11,621 --> 00:00:13,895
And in terms of data protection,
obviously,

7
00:00:13,895 --> 00:00:16,930
we should use encryption
to protect confidentiality.

8
00:00:16,930 --> 00:00:20,030
But we also need to consider
various compliance issues.

9
00:00:20,030 --> 00:00:23,140
These security issues become very
challenging because the clouds

10
00:00:23,140 --> 00:00:25,280
are massively complex systems.

11
00:00:25,280 --> 00:00:27,790
Although the primitives and
common functions are simple,

12
00:00:27,790 --> 00:00:31,110
the complexity comes from the fact
that these primitives and

13
