function units are replicated
thousands of times.

14
00:00:33,740 --> 00:00:36,100
On the other hand,
as we will discuss shortly,

15
00:00:36,100 --> 00:00:40,130
cloud security is a tractable problem
because there are both advantages and

16
00:00:40,130 --> 00:00:43,020
challenges associated
with cloud computing.

17
00:00:43,020 --> 00:00:45,520
Let's first discuss the advantages.

18
00:00:45,520 --> 00:00:49,700
First, you can put public data away
from the internal network to the cloud.

19
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:54,250
And it is easy to manage testing and
security patches when most systems

20
00:00:54,250 --> 00:00:57,240
in a cloud computing environment
use the same software.

21
00:00:57,240 --> 00:01:01,900
And recovery is easy and fast because
it is easy to set up the same system.

22
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:03,690
But there are also challenges.

23
00:01:03,690 --> 00:01:06,360
First, you have to trust
the cloud providers.

24
00:01:06,360 --> 00:01:09,759
And you cannot respond to all
the findings, or investigate directly,

25
00:01:09,759 --> 00:01:14,090
because you have to rely on the cloud
providers who are the direct admins, and

26
00:01:14,090 --> 00:01:17,120
some software running in
the cloud is proprietary.

27
00:01:17,120 --> 00:01:17,960
And finally,

28
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:21,730
there is no physical control of
the computing resources that you use.
